Determine if two expressions are the same. This is different
from testing for equivalence (eg `a == b` and `b == a` are equivalent,
bit not the same).

All errors contain just a `detail` key at the moment.

Validation errors are a special case with the format:

```
{
    "detail": "Invalid request",
    "errors": {
        "field1": ["error 1", "error 2"],
        "field2": ["some error"]
    }
}
```
